# LLM-as-judge for the Cross-System Action workflow. Rename to ``judge.yaml``
# to enable.
#
# Scores the final ``summary`` as an audit record: all FOUR system touches
# (CRM, ERP, ticket, email) must be confirmed IN ORDER, each with its
# reference id. An omitted system or an invented fifth touch is a 0.0. Used
# as the CI eval-gate the pattern's governance leans on.

method: llm_judge

model:
  provider: anthropic/claude-sonnet-4-6
  params:
    temperature: 0.0

rubric: |
  Score the workflow's final summary as the audit record.
    1.0 = all four system touches confirmed in chain order (CRM, ERP,
          ticket, email), each with its reference id
    0.5 = all four touches confirmed but a reference id is missing or the
          order is not stated
    0.0 = a system touch is omitted, an extra touch is invented, or the
          record contradicts the chain

threshold: 0.7
